result.execSummary:
The defendant Kelsey Taylor Elizabet Vavra was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Kelsey Taylor Elizabet Vavra is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Kelsey Taylor Elizabet Vavra was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor [Modifiers: Penalties for Misdemeanors-Class "A"], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
